{"tid":901388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4孩之母藥物敏感昏迷13天離世 夫哀痛：勇敢戰士","createTime":"2018-11-14T03:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T09:56:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb53298b7b23ae099b2a3c9f40e0cb8b5092add6","tid":901388,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=ixLiYFCu732OhaqVDeQPpGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=5c7d6f9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】原打算入住荃灣港安醫院切除「朱古力瘤」的年輕4孩之母謝碧琪(Maggie)，因為術前嚴重藥物敏感一度出現心臟停頓，並陷入昏迷，轉往瑪嘉烈醫院深切治療部留醫，期間一直呈植物人狀態。自本月1日起昏迷的她搏鬥13天後終敵不過死神，今午(13日)2時許離世，瑪嘉烈醫院指已將個案轉交死因庭跟進。其夫Kenji在社交網站稱：「沉痛哀悼！勇敢戰士Maggie I love you 老婆！」<br />\n荃灣港安醫院已就上述事件向衞生署呈報。衞生署表示，初步無資料顯示事件符合醫療風險警示事件中的「錯誤處方藥物引致病人永久喪失主要功能或死亡」的定義。該署已要求院方於4星期內提交詳細報告，並會跟進醫院的調查結果。<br />\n事發於上月30日，Maggie因為腹痛到荃灣港安醫院求醫，證實患有俗稱「朱古力瘤」的子宮內膜異位症，該瘤已大至5厘米，需進行手術切除。她當日獲處方抗生素進行消炎及殺菌，但出現耳鳴的副作用，醫生遂於本月1日轉另一抗生素「羅氏芬」(Rocephin)，並安排她於翌日做手術。豈料注射「羅氏芬」後她即感到不適，並出現心臟停頓，經搶救後需靠強心針及呼吸機吊命。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BJWryI203YcOiCAphxHztA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/1a0ca6278833a441e703ee02499a541e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBJWryI203YcOiCAphxHztA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F1a0ca6278833a441e703ee02499a541e&h=221bf221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GH4oKFeq_hlQ8Oa1P0yg8g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/c3e0874f94f115a7e75359d61a8a333e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGH4oKFeq_hlQ8Oa1P0yg8g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2